Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}張りつめた空気が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:23.85,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}高まる鼓動広がってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:30.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深く息吸い込んだなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:35.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう前しか見えないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰も代わる事出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:43.19,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私しか歩けない道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:46.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その涙も全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:49.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}輝きはじめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:54.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:57.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:59.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:02.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:06.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:09.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:11.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:14.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:16.53,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:21.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喜歡著緊張的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:23.85,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}興奮起來走向更廣闊的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:30.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深呼一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:35.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只專注於眼前的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰都無法替代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:43.19,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有我才能前進的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:46.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}連同那份淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:49.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全部開始閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:54.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因此將宿於手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:57.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}盡情揮揚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:59.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果斷地  徑直地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:02.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向著明天全力進發
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:06.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在轉瞬即逝之間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:09.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}實現那夢中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:11.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}無論它多麼虛幻和遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:14.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也絕不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:16.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和僅屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:21.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}竹劍節奏響徹永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是勇次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小珠人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠在家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我明天要休假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把竹劍拿回來打算調養一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過大家怎麼都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為為了幫宮崎同學做特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.34,0:00:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演看得怎麼樣  玩得盡興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小珠她很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.49,0:00:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然是頭一次見  很難得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.69,0:00:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有不同於常日的青春性質的展開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.39,0:00:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為勇次君就是勇次君嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…你們說什麼啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這點並不讓我討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:00:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:34.03,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第21話\N川添珠姬和鈴木凜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德  你為什麼要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.38,0:02:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了打倒你  我再一次從地獄回來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始延長戰吧！布雷巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德  復活了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德是不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  然後這時候爆炸  呯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:04.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈戈爾登場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈戈爾  參上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈戈爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇場版的新角色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是支持施奈德的謎之女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的身份誰也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是個男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇中嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔那裡沒有女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過藤村先生的表演比女性更女性化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前暫時撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼說的話就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴！下會見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次  就要和你結束這場比賽！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨亮你那身鎧甲給我等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  兩位繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底  打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  到此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你看來怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴之流  就請你乾脆地把他做掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那故事不就大變樣了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐一說到施奈德  就整個變了一個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她原來也會那樣笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴巾我放這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  比小珠大一歲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看起來還是比較像大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜  鈴木凜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過大家都叫她小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  往那一站就有種大小姐氣質
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和小珠處好就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子還是太小孩子氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點我想可能差不多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看小姐那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實還真是了不得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…床和地鋪  你要睡哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡地鋪就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在家也這樣睡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡布雷巴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡他哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義的使者  又厲害  還很帥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼面對敵人都不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…鈴木小姐你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我凜就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜你  喜歡施…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,VHD
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點睡吧  明天還要早起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜  明天要幾點起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是7點出場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以6點出發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以5點起床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5點是吧  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和第39話的「淚水中的東西友情」中\N大阪大爆炸中使用的倒計時鐘一樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布雷巴阻止的那個炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那裡得到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼特有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在販賣網站上看到了相同式樣的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止這個定式炸彈的場面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我心中的名場面排名中名列第三呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  那一和二是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然是施奈德初次登場是第一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二是出現必殺施奈颱風的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是施奈德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你心中的名場面又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從10位開始是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超燃的啊  那個武道館決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那話裡面  我非常喜歡在得知敵人就是教劍道的爺爺的時候紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握著劍的手這樣不停地顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那時候  施奈德和布雷巴第一次合作了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是施奈德不出手相助的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴就要在那裡完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我覺得這裡應該會有什麼辦法解決
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:07:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不會輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為布雷巴是正義的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添  看來你還沒注意到布雷巴的弱點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字面上的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且剛才你說得一副好像布雷巴阻止爆炸一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上是施奈德阻止的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事  是布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超劍戰隊BLADE BRAVER！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅還是白？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切斷哪條線才能停止爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒黃色的話就應該是白色了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的占卜是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…到底是哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紅色  布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢才
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色代表末路  終焉的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍士的話  就砍紅色！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BLADE BRAVE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CUTTING END
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  不是布雷巴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼  因為有施奈德的指引才成功的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上不還是施奈德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算布雷巴一個人也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這後面的40話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈颱風！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搞錯了  布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了她而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了祝福！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少磨蹭了！快去！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  沒有施奈德的話  結婚典禮就沒法開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼我的敵人會救助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能親手打倒你們的  只有我而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做個…了斷吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德——！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是令人感動的畫面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施…施奈德他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來處得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴是我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的門「唰」地打開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抓住的人們逃出來後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了阻止他們竹劍插入地面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈戈爾登場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來這裡好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添  吃糖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點  因為是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別礙事的話就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜也是演員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點戲份  只是個逃跑的女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是藤村的錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又舊又鏽的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那找誰替代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人穿得了施奈戈爾的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要刪鏡頭來混過關嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也要有個限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大  這不行啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要破壞孩子的夢想啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  我還行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別硬撐了  藤村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆給別的事務所打電話找個誰來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈戈爾的劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全部都記在腦子裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台詞會在拍好之後再加進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要站著就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐也比較敏捷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之別太勉強自己啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出演啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈戈爾把想要逃走的眾人趕回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:14:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了示眾正準備用竹劍攻擊一個女學生的時候  布雷巴登場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小姐演施奈戈爾的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女學生不就沒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就說不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡要有個女孩子就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要按照預定的行動就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的問題大家會處理好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備開拍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備開拍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救～命～啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在看…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往那跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快往外跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:15:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都將要成為Death Armour復活用的能量源！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐很入戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗的傢伙都將成為竹劍下的屍骸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害啊  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該怎麼做來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈戈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗嘗這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼名堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重拍！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都給我先去冷靜下頭腦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先暫停一會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先暫停一會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫停一會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思啊  導演
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那兩個孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟  是什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擅自做一些劇本裡沒有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我沒能在那裡停止繼續演下去的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看到你  總感覺到心裡有什麼東西不能平靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:16:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到凜你就不由自主的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡  沒有的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更強一些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是施奈德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你是布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  布雷巴從來就沒有敗過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而施奈德在最後的那幾場裡好幾次都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才說布雷巴贏不過施奈德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要重拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可拜託你們了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搶了布雷巴出場的鏡頭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次拍攝開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難以置信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們部的成員會在休息日自發的出勤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就表示大家都很有幹勁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為部長你應該感到高興才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到小珠的加入能一下帶來這麼大的變化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不光是那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你拼命努力的去支撐著這個部也很重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得大家也不會集中在那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大家也不會像現在這樣相識了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你是個很了不起的傢伙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算那樣奉承我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也得不到任何好處啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是想說這些話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事…這種空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氛圍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀…紀梨乃  快拿空氣清新劑來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我是害蟲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡不言敗的你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你那種鼓勵對我是很強的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫瑪莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然能熟練使用二刀流  可見她在體力上非常了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮崎同學鍛煉一下絕對沒有壞處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是瑪莉是凱莉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…好直接
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來做什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫我來做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可以我休息日鍛煉的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我到今天之前都沒見到你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:19:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你在奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:19:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但同樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我會比你奔跑的更多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間的差距不會縮短
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等於呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要贏我是沒可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮崎同學現在就像變了一個人一樣在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會打敗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過不了多久…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我就在想一定有那種可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也會在關東大會出場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關東大會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正要戰  不如就在公開的場合一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見了  親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Adios{\r}\N再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見…話說這不是墨西哥人說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自主練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你是最認真的一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我昨天玩了一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也想確認一下竹劍的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去  禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研修…是去了沖繩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…因為沒時間了  所以就在車站附近買的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在這段時間有發生什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交到新朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但搞不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該叫「對手」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:21:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:21:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪個學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.27,0:22:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有進劍道部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…在關東大會上我們能見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時候…我們再繼續今天的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.49,0:22:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:22.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:27.79,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:34.18,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:55.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:23:02.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:10.14,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.75,0:23:17.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.76,0:23:20.44,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.73,0:23:25.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.77,0:23:32.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:35.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:40.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:48.00,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:22.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:27.79,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中閃耀著的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:34.18,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:55.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗邊光著腳丫  仰望著夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:23:02.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有無法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:10.14,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮現出午時的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.75,0:23:17.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒勞得令人著急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.76,0:23:20.44,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.73,0:23:25.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}閉上眼睛傾聽心中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.77,0:23:32.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然無法得知  它想與我相見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:35.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:40.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光輝而耀眼的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:48.00,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:23:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我出演電影了
